#. Plugin Name of the plugin
msgid "Citatly - Daily Quote"
msgstr "Citatly – Tägliches Zitat"

#. Description of the plugin
msgid "CPT for quotes + display as quote of the day (AJAX/REST, cache-safe)."
msgstr "CPT für Zitate + Ausgabe als Zitat des Tages (AJAX/REST, cache-sicher)."

